  <name>Linux Wallpaper Engine GUI</name>
  <summary>Manage and apply dynamic wallpapers on Linux</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Linux Wallpaper Engine GUI is a modern, responsive graphical interface for managing 
      dynamic wallpapers on Linux systems. It provides an intuitive way to browse, organize, 
      and apply wallpapers from Wallpaper Engine.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Visual gallery with thumbnail previews</li>
      <li>Group organization and favorites system</li>
      <li>Random wallpaper rotation with customizable intervals</li>
      <li>Window mode with custom resolutions</li>
      <li>Always-on-top control and advanced sound options</li>
      <li>Real-time logging and persistent configuration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
